

{"id":4406,"date":"2023-06-13T14:18:48","date_gmt":"2023-06-13T07:18:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=4406"},"modified":"2023-07-13T10:40:28","modified_gmt":"2023-07-13T03:40:28","slug":"ban-co-can-phai-detox-khong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/ban-co-can-phai-detox-khong\/","title":{"rendered":"B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i detox kh\u00f4ng? 7 g\u1ee3i \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea1ng, t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y hay tr\u00e0 th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c. C\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn nh\u01b0 gan, th\u1eadn, ru\u1ed9t v\u00e0 ph\u1ed5i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i, ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea3i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n hay t\u1eeb kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed. V\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i <strong>detox<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng? Khi n\u00e0o th\u00ec c\u1ea7n detox?<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><br \/>\nT\u1ea1i sao m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p detox th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c?<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c l\u00fd do th\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ea7y h\u01a1i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean, h\u00e3y th\u1eed 7 g\u1ee3i \u00fd d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y thay v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p detox:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1\/ \u0102n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y v\u00e0 rau c\u1ee7\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4537\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4537\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4537 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/an-nhieu-trai-cay-va-rau-cu.png\" alt=\"detox, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/an-nhieu-trai-cay-va-rau-cu.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/an-nhieu-trai-cay-va-rau-cu-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/an-nhieu-trai-cay-va-rau-cu-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/an-nhieu-trai-cay-va-rau-cu-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/an-nhieu-trai-cay-va-rau-cu-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/an-nhieu-trai-cay-va-rau-cu-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4537\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0102n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y v\u00e0 rau c\u1ee7<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y v\u00e0 rau c\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vitamin, kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 vitamin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ung th\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2\/ B\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4540\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4540\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4540 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-day-du-chat-xo.png\" alt=\"detox, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-day-du-chat-xo.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-day-du-chat-xo-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-day-du-chat-xo-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-day-du-chat-xo-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-day-du-chat-xo-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-day-du-chat-xo-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4540\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ti\u00eau h\u00f3a, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ed5 sung 18g ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y trong khi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n 30g.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u1ed3 \u0103n gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y no h\u01a1n sau khi \u0103n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 ti\u00eam m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ru\u1ed9t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3\/ Gi\u1ea3m vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cafein, \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e3 qua ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4529\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4529\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4529 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/giam-viec-su-dung-do-uong-co-con.png\" alt=\"detox, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/giam-viec-su-dung-do-uong-co-con.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/giam-viec-su-dung-do-uong-co-con-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/giam-viec-su-dung-do-uong-co-con-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/giam-viec-su-dung-do-uong-co-con-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/giam-viec-su-dung-do-uong-co-con-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/giam-viec-su-dung-do-uong-co-con-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4529\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Gi\u1ea3m vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cafein, \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e3 qua ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Cafein \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 an to\u00e0n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh n\u1ebfu b\u1ed5 sung 400mg m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi 2-4 ly caf\u00e9. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ed5 sung h\u01a1n 400mg m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7, \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u00e0 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cafein s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean m\u00e0 v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c caf\u00e9 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Enzyme trong gan chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n th\u00e0nh n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00e0 carbon dioxit, \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1eadm. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 v\u1edbi li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00ean s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tim m\u1ea1ch hay ung th\u01b0. Gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ed3n n\u1ea1p v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n \u0111\u00e3 qua ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn bao g\u1ed3m vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m r\u1ee7i ro b\u1ecb ung th\u01b0. Thay \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n \u0111\u00e3 qua ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn b\u1eb1ng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m nguy\u00ean c\u00e1m, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y v\u00e0 rau c\u1ee7, s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam vitamin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng hay gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">4\/ C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 s\u00e2u<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4531\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4531\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4531 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/co-nhung-giac-ngu-sau.png\" alt=\"detox, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/co-nhung-giac-ngu-sau.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/co-nhung-giac-ngu-sau-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/co-nhung-giac-ngu-sau-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/co-nhung-giac-ngu-sau-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/co-nhung-giac-ngu-sau-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/co-nhung-giac-ngu-sau-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4531\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 s\u00e2u<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 n\u00e3o b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i trong gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean c\u1ea3 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng s\u00e2u l\u00e0 nhanh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 t\u1eadp trung, c\u00f2n d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn huy\u1ebft \u00e1p cao, b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 tim m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ti\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">5\/ B\u1ed5 sung h\u1ec7 vi sinh v\u1eadt cho d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4535\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4535\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4535 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-he-vi-sinh-vat-cho-da-day.png\" alt=\"detox, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-he-vi-sinh-vat-cho-da-day.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-he-vi-sinh-vat-cho-da-day-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-he-vi-sinh-vat-cho-da-day-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-he-vi-sinh-vat-cho-da-day-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-he-vi-sinh-vat-cho-da-day-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-he-vi-sinh-vat-cho-da-day-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4535\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ed5 sung h\u1ec7 vi sinh v\u1eadt cho d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng ru\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee9a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i vi khu\u1ea9n, nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i vi khu\u1ea9n hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 vi sinh v\u1eadt n\u00e0y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tr\u00ed n\u00e3o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ed5 sung men vi sinh v\u00e0 prebiotic gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn l\u1ee3i khu\u1ea9n \u1edf trong d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, k\u00edch th\u00edch h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Prebiotic l\u00e0 1 lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 m\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, nh\u01b0ng ti\u00eau h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c vi khu\u1ea9n trong d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn l\u1ee3i khu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. Y\u1ebfn m\u1ea1ch hay qu\u1ea3 m\u1ecdng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n cung c\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 prebiotic.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Men vi sinh l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9c \u0103n ch\u1ee9a vi khu\u1ea9n s\u1ed1ng, b\u1ed5 sung men vi sinh gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ee3i khu\u1ea9n, r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1ng sinh. C\u00e1c th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00ean men nh\u01b0 s\u1eefa chua l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n cung c\u1ea5p men vi sinh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">6\/ T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4937\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4937\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4937 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao.png\" alt=\"detox, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4937\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t mang l\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c. C\u00e1c l\u1ee3i \u00edch bao g\u1ed3m ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng, gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u r\u1ee7i ro ti\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tu\u00fdp 2, gi\u1ea3m tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ung th\u01b0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">7\/ B\u1ed5 sung nhi\u1ec1u n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4935\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4935\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4935 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-nhieu-nuoc-1.png\" alt=\"detox, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-nhieu-nuoc-1.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-nhieu-nuoc-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-nhieu-nuoc-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-nhieu-nuoc-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/bo-sung-nhieu-nuoc-1-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4935\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">U\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Kho\u1ea3ng 60% c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. B\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u00edch cho th\u1eadn, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/10-thuc-pham-giam-can-ban-nen-them-vao-thuc-don-ngay\/\">10 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n b\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u00eam v\u00e0o th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n ngay<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/nen-tap-gym-bao-l